author: Literature Devil
description:
What if a killer could steal your soul?

👉 Back Lady Midnight: Devils Dwell in Silent Springs now on IndieGoGo and start the hunt. https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/lady-midnight-devils-dwell-in-silent-springs-b-w/x/22169562#/

After her best friend’s father leaps to his death — crimson tears streaming from his eyes — Midnight takes the case. Poisoned? Cursed? Either way, his suicide was meant to keep his soul safe from his murderer’s hands. Because in dark magic, a killer can claim the souls he takes.

Her investigation leads to the Dream City Strangler — an infamous undead serial killer — but the truth runs deeper. The curse, the poison, the bloody tears… they’re far too sophisticated for him. The mystery is spiraling into a supernatural conspiracy, and the true mastermind remains at large.

If you love occult detective stories, supernatural thrillers, horror comics, or indie noir graphic novels, don’t miss this one.
title: Occult Detective Comic | Lady Midnight: Devils Dwell in Silent Springs
